metadata.name: Goda Claim #1
metadata.description: All Mint Pass Holders will be able to claim a giveaway ticket - every holder will receive an NFT with some artwork. The winning NFTs will receive a GOLD background version with metadata that says “Winner”. Snapshot was taking on 11/15. Mint Pass holders will have until the end of the auction to claim. Winners will receive the Hilma piece before reveal on Friday the 18th.
